96
00:09:24,719 --> 00:09:28,280
- I'm exactly the opposite... - How long have I been staying here?

97
00:09:28,355 --> 00:09:30,585
- A couple of days. - And you're holding my calls?

98
00:09:30,658 --> 00:09:34,059
- Like you said. - Okay, but this guy's an exception.

99
00:09:34,128 --> 00:09:38,030
- Do you know this guy? - Yeah, it's your friend, right?

100
00:09:38,099 --> 00:09:40,727
What makes you think he's my friend?

101
00:09:40,801 --> 00:09:43,235
- I just saw you together, that's all. - He's not my friend.

102
00:09:43,304 --> 00:09:45,864
- Okay. - If he calls or if he shows up here,

103
00:09:45,940 --> 00:09:48,534
you give me a call in my room, okay?

104
00:09:48,609 --> 00:09:50,873
- What, his name's Teddy? - Teddy, yeah.

105
00:09:50,945 --> 00:09:52,970
All right.

106
00:09:53,047 --> 00:09:56,710
Look, I hope my condition's not gonna be a problem for you.

107
00:09:56,784 --> 00:09:59,719
No, not as long as you remember to pay the bill.

108
00:09:59,787 --> 00:10:02,415
- Okay. - Forty.

109
00:10:04,625 --> 00:10:07,458
This guy...

110
00:10:07,528 --> 00:10:10,554
He's here already.

111
00:10:10,631 --> 00:10:12,565
Lenny!

112
00:10:14,268 --> 00:10:17,829
[Narrating] You really need a system if you're gonna make it work.

113
00:10:17,905 --> 00:10:21,136
You kind of learn to trust your own handwriting.

114
00:10:21,208 --> 00:10:24,109
That becomes an important part of your life. You write yourself notes.

115
00:10:24,178 --> 00:10:26,544
And where you put your notes... That also becomes important.

116
00:10:26,614 --> 00:10:30,175
You need a jacket that's got like six pockets in it.

117
00:10:30,251 --> 00:10:32,879
Particular pockets for particular things.

118
00:10:32,953 --> 00:10:36,753
You just kind of learn to know where things go and how the system works.

119
00:10:36,824 --> 00:10:41,591
You have to be wary of other people writing stuff for you, that it's gonna lead you astray.

120
00:10:41,662 --> 00:10:45,860
I mean, I don't know how these people try and take advantage of somebody with this condition.

121
00:10:45,933 --> 00:10:50,734
If you have a piece of information which is vital,

122
00:10:50,805 --> 00:10:54,639
writing on your body instead of on a piece of paper can be the answer.

123
00:10:54,708 --> 00:10:57,006
It's just a permanent way of keeping a note.

124
00:10:57,077 --> 00:10:59,307
[Phone Ringing]

125
00:11:04,185 --> 00:11:05,982
