136
00:12:30,571 --> 00:12:33,563
[Thinking] Discount Inn.

137
00:12:33,641 --> 00:12:36,405
Natalie.

138
00:12:37,978 --> 00:12:41,175
My car.

139
00:12:41,248 --> 00:12:43,512
Teddy.

