163
00:16:30,878 --> 00:16:35,508
Well, Sammy wrote himself endless amounts of notes, but he got mixed up.

164
00:16:35,582 --> 00:16:40,019
I have a more graceful solution to the memory problem.

165
00:16:42,322 --> 00:16:44,790
