174
00:17:42,749 --> 00:17:46,685
- I'm sorry. I should have explained. I have this... - You did explain, Lenny.

175
00:17:46,753 --> 00:17:49,153
Please call me Leonard. My wife called me Lenny.

176
00:17:49,223 --> 00:17:52,818
