00:19:27,321 --> 00:19:30,290
Tell me about her again.

206
00:19:30,357 --> 00:19:32,325
Why?

207
00:19:32,392 --> 00:19:35,156
Because you like to remember her.

208
00:19:37,064 --> 00:19:41,592
She was beautiful. To me, she was perfect.

209
00:19:41,668 --> 00:19:46,332
No. Don't just recite the words.

210
00:19:46,406 --> 00:19:51,070
Close your eyes... and remember her.

211
