00:21:09,990 --> 00:21:12,220
- I'm sorry. - It's okay.

226
00:21:12,292 --> 00:21:16,353
"See, you have this condition." [Laughs]

227
00:21:16,430 --> 00:21:20,389
Oh, are you still staying at the Discount Inn, room 304? You left it at my place.

228
00:21:25,972 --> 00:21:29,237
Yeah. [Chuckles]

229
00:21:29,309 --> 00:21:32,073
- They treating you okay? - I don't remember.

230
00:21:32,145 --> 00:21:36,980
[Laughs] You know what we have in common?

231
00:21:38,985 --> 00:21:42,785
We are both survivors.

232
00:21:42,856 --> 00:21:46,348
You take care, Leonard.

233
00:21:53,567 --> 00:21:57,594
